          <lg n="1">
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-327-967O-line-1" n="1">As Thomas was cudgell'd one day, by his wife,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-327-967O-line-2" n="2">He took to his heels &amp; ran for his life;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-327-967O-line-3" n="3">Tom's three dearest friends came by in the squabble,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-327-967O-line-4" n="4">And skreen'd him at once from the shrew &amp; the rabble;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-327-967O-line-5" n="5">Then ventur'd to give him some wholesome advice:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-327-967O-line-6" n="6">But Tom is a fellow of humour so nice,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-327-967O-line-7" n="7">Too proud to be counsel'd, too wise to take warning,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-327-967O-line-8" n="8">He sent to all three a challenge next morning:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-327-967O-line-9" n="9">He fought with all three, thrice ventur'd his life;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-327-967O-line-10" n="10">Then went home again, &amp; was thrash'd by his wife.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
